oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Building on Broadway
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:subject: Hatch Show Print (Firm);
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: A color photo featuring construction being done on a building in downtown Nashville on 4th Avenue and Broadway. A painted sign on the building says, "Broadway Furniture Co. Bargain Corner 8 Big Floors New and Used Furniture." Hatch Show Print was located across the street from this building on 4th Avenue, probably close to the location this photo was taken.
